 <BR>
 
 In this mode you can insert and remove inner nodes. For inserting inner nodes, select those
 nodes you want to become children of the new inner node, then press the right mouse button.
 The new children need to have a common parent. The first picture below shows a correct splitting,
 the second one an incorrect splitting.
